<title>ạlậb yʿlm</title>
<aka>lmạ tnwʾ bạlfsẖl</aka>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1-lmạ tnwʾ bạlfsẖl
 lmạ ysạwr ạlmll
 dẖw ạlḥq yʿṭyk ạlạml .. ạlậb yʿlm

[C1]
   ạlqrạr- (ạlậb yʿlm)
   ạ̉kẖy ạbtsm .. bh ạʿtṣm .. (ạlậb yʿlm)

[V2]
 2-ạ̹n jạʾk kẖṭb ʿṣyb
 ạ̉w jzt ywmạaⁿ fy lhyb
 lạ tkẖsẖy̱ mn ḥml ạlṣlyb .. fạlậb yʿlm

[V3]
 3-ạ̹n ḥl ḍyq yḍṭrm
 ạ̉w rạḥ kẖwf ylthm
 ạ̉mạm hdẖạ fạ̹btsm .. fạlậb yʿlm</lyrics>
</song>